Clean Space 2015.03 Multilingual [4realtorrentz]



Have you ever felt embarrassed when others sit before your PC and find out where you've been on web, what media you played, what applications you used? Let the trouble go with the wind by using Clean Space now! Once you try it and you will understand its exactly the tool you are looking for to erase the traces of your activity through PC.

This easy and powerful program will stop you getting worried that someone can see sites you visit or reveal your online/offline secrets. It is also useful if you do not want your computer to keep tones of temporary files or maintain cache of viewed files.

Whats the danger?
If you do want to protect your privacy, Clean Space is the tool you need. It was designed to clear user browsing history, clean index.dat files, remove cookies, cache, logs, delete temporary internet files, autocomplete search history and any other tracks that user leaves after using PC. All you have to do is download the tool and allow it to clear the tracks about your activity. Be sure, no user documents will be deleted by mistake! Before starting the process you have got the possibility to preview the tracks and garbage files that are about to be removed. They are represented in the form of a list separated by areas. Simple double click on any item in the list and you see what it stores, for example cookies or index.dat files, then you can clear them all or just selectively.

We offer you the possibility to obtain a free trial version of this software, thus you will be able to find yourself how many invisible areas are hidden in Windows that record your activity in all means! Clean Space also contains some additional built-in tools, like for example Screen Lock that will take care to protect your privacy.

New program suppoprt
Smart program support makes possible to clear tracks both in Windows XP and Vista as well as in the most popular browsers (IE, FireFox, Opera, Chrome), and in many other programs that you use. Every month new version comes that help Clean Space recognize and clear tracks in newly released software.

Deleting without recovery!
Unlike many existent programs, Clean Space includes such extremely important features as irrecoverable file deletion based on the DODD 5220.22 (Gutmann, Russian GOST) algorithms and file names-shredding. Give a try now!
